  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538350/extras/e77722c73107e4a51dafe41d99e2ff79.avif?t=1749239777\" width=600 height=375 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A strategic yet fast-paced arcade-styled shooter with roguelike elements!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the story of 4 self-proclaimed heroes as they fight the injustice of the \"Earth Unit\" -  a collaborative government created by the people of Earth in an effort to keep their dying planet from becoming nothing but a memory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538350/extras/9f6ac6630ea4e15d073f6c19ab8957af.poster.avif?t=1749239777\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538350/extras/9f6ac6630ea4e15d073f6c19ab8957af.webm?t=1749239777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538350/extras/9f6ac6630ea4e15d073f6c19ab8957af.mp4?t=1749239777\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Arcade-styled shooter action with a unique upgrade system!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Real-time strategy overworld map that runs non-stop while you play!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Randomized enemy placements, spawns, and upgrade chips!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Fully voiced dialogue with colorful characters! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Neato blips and beeps!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Unique and engaging boss battles, each with vivid personalities!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538350/extras/b08c9face5f7f0724be145f5790e2798.poster.avif?t=1749239777\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538350/extras/b08c9face5f7f0724be145f5790e2798.webm?t=1749239777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538350/extras/b08c9face5f7f0724be145f5790e2798.mp4?t=1749239777\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your support is what drives this game!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The dev would love to hear from you, and thank you for your support!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Cover art by the amazing Hare Candy Art!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Trailer music by the talented Will Dodson!</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538350/extras/e77722c73107e4a51dafe41d99e2ff79.avif?t=1749239777\" width=600 height=375 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A strategic yet fast-paced arcade-styled shooter with roguelike elements!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the story of 4 self-proclaimed heroes as they fight the injustice of the \"Earth Unit\" -  a collaborative government created by the people of Earth in an effort to keep their dying planet from becoming nothing but a memory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538350/extras/9f6ac6630ea4e15d073f6c19ab8957af.poster.avif?t=1749239777\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538350/extras/9f6ac6630ea4e15d073f6c19ab8957af.webm?t=1749239777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538350/extras/9f6ac6630ea4e15d073f6c19ab8957af.mp4?t=1749239777\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Arcade-styled shooter action with a unique upgrade system!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Real-time strategy overworld map that runs non-stop while you play!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Randomized enemy placements, spawns, and upgrade chips!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Fully voiced dialogue with colorful characters! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Neato blips and beeps!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Unique and engaging boss battles, each with vivid personalities!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538350/extras/b08c9face5f7f0724be145f5790e2798.poster.avif?t=1749239777\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538350/extras/b08c9face5f7f0724be145f5790e2798.webm?t=1749239777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538350/extras/b08c9face5f7f0724be145f5790e2798.mp4?t=1749239777\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your support is what drives this game!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The dev would love to hear from you, and thank you for your support!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Cover art by the amazing Hare Candy Art!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Trailer music by the talented Will Dodson!</i></p>",
